        sprite.x += delta.x
        sprite.y += delta.y
    }
}, this)
```

Check if available with `cc.sys.capabilities.accelerometer`. Then use the acceleration event:
```js
cc.eventManager.addListener({
    event: cc.EventListener.ACCELERATION,
    callback: (accelEvent) => {
        // accelEvent.x, .y, .z, .timestamp
        node.x += accelEvent.x * speed
    }
}, this)
```
Mostly useful on mobile devices for tilt controls.

